Breakfast lovers, this one’s for you! 🥞✨ Packed in our favorite @omielifeinc lunchbox:⁠
⁠
Nutella French-toast roll-ups (recipe below!), strawberries, yogurt with birthday cake cookie crumbs, Mango Juice, and Breakfast Bar. ⁠
⁠
⁠
Nutella French-Toast Roll-Ups (makes 6)⁠
⁠
Flatten bread slices with a rolling pin; trim the crusts.⁠
Spread Nutella, roll tightly.⁠
Whisk 2 eggs, ¼ cup milk, ½ tsp cinnamon, splash of vanilla.⁠
Dip rolls, pan-fry in butter until golden on all sides.⁠
Let cool, then pack ’em up!⁠
Easy to prep, fun to eat, and keeps everything right where it belongs! ⁠
⁠

I’m a busy mom of two curious, creative girls who keep me on my toes and keep our lunchbox game strong. I love finding ways to make mealtime fun, colorful, and stress-free while sneaking in a little learning and love along the way.⁠

We’ve been using OmieBox for YEARS and once you try it, you’ll get why. From warm meals to cool snacks, it’s the only lunchbox that truly keeps up with our busy, on-the-go family.⁠
